text: Well it is super fun. You unlock new characters and there is different levels and events.And I love it when my mom and I play it and see who can go the longest. The first times we were doing it I kept dying or getting hit by the train since I kept looking at my mom’s screen.Since we started doing the challenges like a week ago . title: Diego’s PRIME game
text: I’m a huge fan of playing subway surfers, it’s my favorite way to take my mind off of all my rough days at school because it’s free to play and you don’t need WiFi or cell service, my favorite part of the game is unlocking new characters, outfits, and boards, I can’t wait for all the new future updates, download subways surfers and join me in the endless running fun

title: Would recommend it 100 percent!!! 😍
text: I would recommend this game because it is very fun. I would like you to get it because even though it has some ads it is barely any 😍. Even though I am stuck in the bronze on the leaderboard I still have a lot of fun!!! Another reason why I recommend it is because you get to see different things when the game changes depending on holidays and stuff like that. It is very fun and even though people give it four stars, I would give it five.   Also, the music is really fun and it also changes. So that is why I think you should download Subway surfers!!!! 🤩🤩
